          <a name="id2177912"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS72"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Special Attacks:</strong></span> A skeleton retains none of the base creature's special attacks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2177941"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS73"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Special Qualities:</strong></span> A skeleton loses most special qualities of the base creature. It retains any extraordinary special qualities that improve its melee or ranged attacks. A skeleton gains the following special qualities.</p>
          <p><span class="emphasis"><em>Immunity to Cold (Ex):</em></span> Skeletons are not affected by cold.</p>
          <p><span class="emphasis"><em>Damage Reduction 5/Bludgeoning:</em></span> Skeletons lack flesh or internal organs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2177986"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
