          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS74"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Saves:</strong></span> Base save bonuses are Fort +1/3 HD, Ref +1/3 HD, and Will +1/2 HD + 2.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2178015"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS75"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Abilities:</strong></span> A skeleton's Dexterity increases by +2, it has no Constitution or Intelligence score, its Wisdom changes to 10, and its Charisma changes to 1.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
